text: György Keleti (18 May 1946 – 13 September 2020) was a Hungarian politician. He was Minister of Defence between 1994 and 1998 during the Gyula Horn cabinet. From 1992 to 2010, he was a member of the National Assembly. He was born in Lučenec, Czechoslovakia. Keleti died on 13 September 2020 from a long-illness in Budapest, aged 74. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Hungarian politicians
